erif;\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:Vrinda;\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 107%;\">Impact of Technology In Human Life</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">Over the years, technology has revolutionized our world and daily lives. Additionally, technology has created amazing tools, devices, facilities and resources, putting useful information at our fingertips and increase the convenience of our lives.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">Modern technology has paved the way for multi-functional devices like the smartphone. Computers, smartwatch, smart gadgets and so on are increasingly faster, more portable, and higher-powered than ever before. With all of these revolutions, technology has also made our lives easier, faster, better, and more fun.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">The wind of change in multiple sectors of human life: </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">Technology has upgraded the standard of living and saved our valuable time through different advance services. To understand it better let&rsquo;s see what are the changes happened in our life in Bangladesh from the year 2000-2021 (last 20 years). </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Entertainment &amp; Advertisement Sector: </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">We used watch drama, movies, advertisements in TV and television used to be the only device of entertainment in our life. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: +mn-ea; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">Now in 2021, entertainment has come into our smartphones and smart TVs. Now we have different OTT platforms and YouTube to watch content and advertisement media has shifted from television channels to Facebook &amp; YouTube</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: +mn-ea; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">. </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">Back in 2000 when communication was in billboard because we used to look around when we were outside. Now in 2021, the advertisement has shifted into our smartphones because we prefer internet browsing whenever we are outside now a days. Billboard has turned into Facebook static</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">We used to read new paper every morning and that is the reason why newspaper was the most important media of print advertisement. </span><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">Now in 2021, the advertisement has shifted into online news portals. Now a days people check news through their smartphones and that&rsquo;s why most of the renown newspapers have their online version of it.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: +mn-ea; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">To communicate the promotional &amp; sales offer we used to distribute leaflets. Even in front of the trade fair Bangladesh we used to see BPs standing and distributing leaflets among the customer. </span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: +mn-ea; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">Now the banners, leaflets and other print form of advertisements have turned into GDN banners and targeting has become more precise and to the point. Where we can place the ads of a sport brand right beside the sports news and garb the attention of sports enthusiast.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">20 years back we never thought of to attend classes and obtain education without going to school, college and universities physically. Now in 2021, students are attending classes online through smartphones, laptops and desktops by dint of technology.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-