t-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">For regular grocery and any other shopping, we had to go to the shops/market to buy. We used to spend a long span of time forgoing one shop to another and shop. </span><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">Now the market is in our phone. We just need to scroll, choose &amp; click and product gets delivered at our home. Again, it&rsquo;s just a click away. We can purchase products from anywhere of the globe.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">To order food from outside, we had to go to restaurants and place the order. </span><span style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">Now we don&rsquo;t need to go out to order food from outside. All restaurants are in our phone now a days. It&rsquo;s just a click away to order food and get it delivered at home.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:RelyOnVML/>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>BN</w:LidThemeComplexS