mal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong>Mobile Phone user: </strong>Back in 2000 there were only 0.28 million people in Bangladesh who used to have a mobile phone and now there are 171.854 million people in Bangladesh are using mobile phone. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong>Internet User: </strong>Only 0.1 % of the entire population of Bangladesh was under the light of internet back in 2000 but now, there are 28% of the entire population is actively using internet through various devices.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong>E-Commerce</strong>: Bangladesh&rsquo;s e-commerce market stands at $1.6 billion currently and will double to $3 billion by 2023. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times;\"><strong>Digital Transactions:</strong> Total transactions through MFSs increased from BDT321 billion in December 2018 to BDT448 billion in June 2020, an increase of around 40%.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"color: #313131; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: times new roman, times;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:Sav