(1, '<h2 class=\"uppercase\">About TechHut</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">TechHut is an online market place of tech products. It is established on the aim to provide 100% genuine technological products with the highest customer satisfaction priority to the tech lover consumers in Bangladesh. Tech Hut will be operating as an online e-commerce platform only. Virtual Market Solutions Limited is the parent company of TechHut. It will be conducted and operated by the executive body of VMSL. The head office is located in Gulshan Circle-1, Dhaka, Bangladesh.Trade License Number- 004757</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"uppercase\">Mission Statement</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tech Hut&rsquo;s mission is to sell compact, portable and convenient technological devices with inclusion of global brands to satisfy the growing need of exclusivity in Bangladesh market.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"uppercase\">Vision</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To become the market leader in the field of nanotechnology e-commerce in Bangladesh by providing the fastest delivery, secured payment system and user-friendly interface.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>OVERVIEW</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This website is operated by Virtual Market Solution Limited (registered name of TechHut). The terms &ldquo;We&rdquo;, &ldquo;Us&rdquo; and &ldquo;Our&rdquo; are used to refer to only TechHut or Virtual Market Solution Limited offers all information, tools and services which are used or concerns TechHut carrying out of business, and are publicly available at the website. The user shall be deemed to have accepted all the terms, conditions, policies and notices officially stated, as they continue to use the website and its services.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: jus