(252, 'Anker PowerWave 7.5 Pad with Quick Charge 3.0 Charger', 'B2514L21', 'anker-powerwave-75-pad-with-quick-charge-30-charger', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 28, 1, 1, 1, '4680', '5180', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630137701736556285.jpg,1630137775157822603.jpg,1630137775709323157.jpg,1630137775871732950.jpg,1630137775384860806.jpg,1630137775833676274.jpg,1630137775833886604.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@wpb_text_column wpb_content_element@>\r\n<div class=@wpb_wrapper@>\r\n<p>The High-Speed Wireless Charging Pad</p>\r\n<p><strong>PowerWave 7.5 Pad</strong></p>\r\n<p>An expanded charging surface, adaptive technology, and advanced safety systems combine to create PowerWave, the premiere wireless charger from Anker.</p>\r\n<p>Advanced technology detects your wireless charge-compatible devices, delivering up to 7.5W for Apple devices, and 10W for Samsung. A state-of-the-art internal cooling fan prevents overheating and slowdown, maintaining high-speed charging from 0% to full.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Anti-Slip Surface</li>\r\n<li>Case-Friendly Charging</li>\r\n<li>State-of-the-Art Internal Cooling</li>\r\n<li>MultiProtect Safety System</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper tabs-layout-tabs@>\r\n<div class=@woodmart-tab-wrapper@>\r\n<div id=@tab-dwspecs_product_specifications@ class=@woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--dwspecs_product_specifications panel entry-content wc-tab@>\r\n<div class=@wc-tab-inner \r\n										@>\r\n<div class=@@>\r\n<div class=@dwspecs-product-table@>\r\n<div class=@dwspecs-product-table-group@>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Brand</td>\r\n<td>Anker</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Model</td>\r\n<td>B2514L21</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Color Selection</td>\r\n<td>White</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Input</td>\r\n<td>12V / 1.5A</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Output</td>\r\n<td>5W / 7.5W / 10W</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Size</td>\r\n<td>4.3 x 4.3 x 0.7 inches</td>