(254, 'Anker SoundCore Flare 2 (Black)', '07384391', 'anker-soundcore-flare-2-black-1', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 25, 1, 1, 1, '5795', '6190', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630234365369025884.jpg,1630234450438358883.jpg,1630234450346865113.jpg,1630234450914679337.jpg,1630234451857460801.jpg,1630234451542852413.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>360&deg; Immersive Sound:&nbsp;</strong>A portable Bluetooth speaker with Powerful 360&deg;, bass-driven audio. Dual drivers and passive radiators combine with BassUp&trade; technology to generate a portable party with 20W of intense sound.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Beat-Driven Light Show:&nbsp;</strong>A totally reimagined rainbow light show that pulses, phases, and shines to the beat of your music. Double light-rings simultaneously shine down onto the dancefloor and up into the atmosphere for pumping floor-to-ceiling illumination.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pool Party Proof:&nbsp;</strong>No matter where the music needs to be, Flare 2 portable Bluetooth speaker&nbsp;is suited up and ready. Super-safe IPX7 waterproof protection effortlessly withstands spills, rain, and even complete submersion in water.</p>\r\n<p><strong>PartyCast Technology:</strong>&nbsp;Link 100+ Flare 2 portable Bluetooth speakers to party into the next dimension&mdash;sound and light synchronize across every speaker for a seamlessly electrifying experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customize The Atmosphere:&nbsp;</strong>Enhance your audio with complete EQ control then tailor the light show to your mood with 6 mesmerizing lighting modes.</p>', '<div class=@pdp-general-features@>\r\n<p><strong><span class=@key-title@> Brand :</span></strong> Anker</p>\r\n<p><strong><span class=@key-title@> Speakers Config : </span></strong>20 W</p>\r\n<p><strong><span class=@key-title@> Bluetooth : </span></strong>Yes</p>\r\n<p><strong><span class=@key-title@> Model : </span></strong>SoundCore Flare 2</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@box-content@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i1.58cb7690b9AvLG@><strong><span class=@key-title@>What&rsquo;s in the box : </span></strong>Flare 2, Happy card Quick Start Guide, USB-A to USB-C Cable</div>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 07:01:14', '2021-09-18 08:42:30', NULL, NULL),
(255, 'Anker Soundcore Flare B2C - UN Black Iteration 1', 'A3161011', 'anker-soundcore-flare-b2c-un-black-iteration-1', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 25, 1, 1, 1, '4725', '5100', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630234896476482527.jpg,1630234896827430311.jpg,1630234896848058755.jpg,1630234896764144371.jpg,1630234897950567784.jpg,1630234897925555549.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span class=@a-list-item@>Incredible Sound Loved by 20 Million+ People</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>All Round Pounding Sound:</strong> Intense 360&deg; sound drops from back-to-back 5W (10W total) neodymium drivers for stunning sound in every direction&mdash;all powered by BassUp technology, multi-band DRC, and dual IIR passive radiators. Put the sound at the centre of your house party and give everyone front-row thrills.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>Audio Fireworks:</strong> A halo of LEDs phase, pulse, and glow with the rhythm of your music for a next-level listening experience. Fill your house or yard with a personalized party atmosphere; 8 individual LEDs and 5 lighting modes offer complete customization.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>Pool Party Proof:</strong> No matter where the good times go, Flare Mini is an outdoor Bluetooth speaker that is suited up and ready. Super-safe IPX7 waterproof protection withstands spills, rain, and even complete submersion (for 30 minutes) in water.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>Can&rsquo;t Stop The Beat:</strong> A high-efficiency Li-ion battery ensures you get 12 hours of thumping sound and pulsing light from a single charge&mdash;longer than ordinary outdoor Bluetooth speakers.Start the party early, and go to bed late!</span></p>', '<div style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px; white-space: pre-wrap;@>\r\n<div style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px; white-space: pre-wrap;@>\r\n<div style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px; white-space: pre-wrap;@>\r\n<p><span style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.0px; padding: 0.0px; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px;@>360&deg; Sound &amp; BassUp Mode</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.0px; padding: 0.0px; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px;@>Beat-Driven Light Show</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.0px; padding: 0.0px; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px;@>Wireless Stereo Pairing</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=@box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.0px; padding: 0.0px; border: 0.0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14.0px;@>Works with the Soundcore App</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 07:18:13', '2021-09-18 08:42:57', NULL, NULL),
(256, 'Soundcore 3 B2C- UN Black iteration 1', '97943026', 'soundcore-3-b2c-un-black-iteration-1', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 25, 1, 1, 1, '5450', '5850', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630236781423159717.jpg,1630236782977042057.jpg,1630236782375640557.jpg,1630236782955088611.jpg,1630236782930373299.jpg,1630236782859030218.jpg,1630236782448410113.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@description content@>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>Upgraded Driver Technology:</strong>&nbsp;Soundcore 3 Bluetooth speaker has dual drivers with 100% pure titanium diaphragms that extend treble up to 40kHz and minimize distortion.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>Enhanced Bass:</strong>&nbsp;Dual passive radiators and upgraded BassUp technology work in tandem to pump up the bass in real-time&mdash;even at low volumes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>16W Stereo Sound:</strong>&nbsp;Soundcore 3&rsquo;s stereo sound makes your music sound more immersive and pumps up the atmosphere in both indoors and outdoor spaces.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>24-Hour Playtime:</strong>&nbsp;Soundcore 3 Bluetooth speaker is perfect for taking on days out or weekends away thanks to its ultra-long playtime that lets you listen to up to 480 songs on a single charge.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-list-item@><strong>IPX7 Waterproof:</strong>&nbsp;Drench Soundcore 3 Bluetooth speaker in the shower, submerge it in the pool, or get it soaked on a rainy day&mdash;the IPX7 waterproof case will still protect all the important stuff inside.</span></p>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Colour: Black</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@specCategory_2rDp2@>\r\n<p class=@groupName_3O9-v@>Primary Wireless Connection</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemValue_3FLTX@>Bluetooth</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@specCategory_2rDp2@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=@groupName_3O9-v@>Inputs/Outputs</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>3.5 mm Auxiliary Input</div>\r\n<div class=@itemValue_3FLTX@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>USB Input</div>\r\n<div class=@itemValue_3FLTX@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@specCategory_2rDp2@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=@groupName_3O9-v@>Speaker Features</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Total System Power (Peak): 2 x 3 W</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Shielded Speakers: No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@specCategory_2rDp2@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=@groupName_3O9-v@>Power</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Power Source: Built-in rechargeable battery</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Approximate Battery Life: Up to 24 Hours</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 class=@groupName_3O9-v@>Physical Features</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Width: 4.5 cm</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Height: 5.4 cm</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@itemContainer_uqm6b@>\r\n<div class=@itemName_GaNqp@>Depth: 16.5 cm&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 07:30:52', '2021-09-18 09:32:30', NULL, NULL),
(257, 'Anker SoundCore Icon (Black)', 'A3122H11', 'anker-soundcore-icon-black', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 25, 1, 1, 1, '4010', '4390', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630305898648364491.jpg,1630306517144248386.jpg,1630306518316737271.jpg,1630306518197142524.jpg,1630306518497682621.jpg,1630306518774044357.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>BassUP technology and an over-sized elliptical driver work together to power the soundtrack to your adventure. Icon&rsquo;s detachable strap lets you wrap and hang it anywhere. Railings, trees, clothes, bikes, or anywhere else you can think of. Hang it up, then live it up. Press play, start moving, then see who needs to recharge first. Icon goes for up to 12 hours from a single charge. It&rsquo;s time to get drenched in sound (and water). Icon boasts IP67 water resistance and floats while it plays. Drop the beats. Literally. Icon&rsquo;s robust design will take any abuse you put it through it and keep on playing. If you&rsquo;re going into the wild then your speaker needs to be ready. Fortunately, Icon rounds off its comprehensive protection with super-tough dust-proofing. Cruising the streets, hiking the trails, and chilling on the beach. Icon is ready for all 3, and a whole lot more. Its detachable strap means that it can wrap, hang, and play anywhere you want to. Icon utilizes a single over-sized elliptical driver. This specialized design makes it possible to maximize space and squeeze in even more sound-blasting hardware. The result is a super-compact speaker that can rock any space, whether it&rsquo;s indoors or out. Take journeys, hikes, and adventures to the extreme; Icon is equipped for anything you can throw at it. Its IP67 water-, dust-, and shock-proofing provide super-strong protection. And thanks to its cleverly designed casing, Icon even floats. Not many will be able to keep up with Icon. You&rsquo;ll have to rock hard, loud, and fast for 12 hours if you want to compete. And even if you can match the pace, you&rsquo;ll definitely need longer than 3 hours to recharge.</p>', '<table class=@data-table flex-table@ style=@width: 485px;@ cellspacing=@0@ cellpadding=@0@>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@heading-row@ style=@width: 480.533px;@ colspan=@3@>Main Features</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Type</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Bluetooth v4.2</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Others</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Water Resistance: IP67<br />Wireless Stereo Pairing<br />BassUp Technology</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@heading-row@ style=@width: 480.533px;@ colspan=@3@>Physical Spec</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Dimension</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>8.3 x 4.2 x 2.8 in</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Weight</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>0.78 lb</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Color</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Black</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Connection Type</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Wireless</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@heading-row@ style=@width: 480.533px;@ colspan=@3@>Power Source</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Battery capacity / voltage</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Power: 10 Watts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=@width: 254.167px;@>Battery Life</td>\r\n<td class=@value@ style=@width: 224.133px;@>Playtime: 12 Hours</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@heading-row@ style=@width: 480.533px;@ colspan=@3@>Manufacture Warranty</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=@name@ style=