(258, 'Anker SoundCore Infini Pro', '72013099', 'anker-soundcore-infini-pro', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 25, 1, 1, 1, '18360', '19490', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630237086328275054.jpg,1630237198162412127.jpg,1630237198798031160.jpg,1630237198842065400.jpg,1630237198889001938.jpg,1630237198485228048.jpg,1630237198902973444.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p><strong>Dolby AtmosⓇ:</strong> The world&rsquo;s leading surround sound technology reproduces breathtaking, moving audio from all around you&mdash;even overhead.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Built-In Subwoofers:</strong> Infini Pro&rsquo;s integrated 2.1 channel design pairs two front-facing 2.5-inch mid-range drivers and 1-inch tweeters with dual, up-facing 3-inch built-in subwoofers, symmetrical bass reflex ports, and exclusive BassUp technology for intense low frequencies and 105dB of room-filling sound.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customized Sound Modes:</strong> Choose from Movie, Music, or Voice mode to enhance Infini Pro&rsquo;s sound for the media you&rsquo;re watching or listening to.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile Input Options:</strong> Choose from HDMI, HDMI ARC, optical, or Bluetooth 5.0 connections. Also supports 4K HDR and Dolby Vision pass-through to 4K TVs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Slim Design:</strong> Infini Pro&rsquo;s low profile, streamlined body is 36 inches in length, and is wrapped in a discreet black fabric to allow it to blend in effortlessly with your interior.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@html-content detail-content@>&nbsp;</div>', '<p><span data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i3.1b8b49b9knyKJo@>Soundcore | Hear It. Feel It.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Model number:</strong> A3372</p>\r\n<p>Dolby AtmosⓇ Technology</p>\r\n<p>Dolby Atmos transports you from the ordinary into the extraordinary with breathtaking, moving audio that fills your room and flows above and around you. Using this cutting-edge technology, Infini Pro can reproduce cinema-like sound from a single soundbar.</p>\r\n<p>Cinematic Atmosphere</p>\r\n<p><span data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i4.1b8b49b9knyKJo@>Two built-in 3-inch woofers, 2.5-inch mid-range drivers, and 1-inch tweeters are paired with two bass reflex ports and our exclusive BassUP technology to deliver 105dB of audio power with intense low frequencies.</span></p>\r\n<p>Enhanced Entertainment Experience</p>\r\n<p>Movie Mode: Feel the bass as it reaches new depths, bringing heart-stopping movie moments right into the heart of your home. Dialogue is brought to you with enhanced clarity to ensure you hear every single word.</p>\r\n<p>Music Mode: Treble is enhanced, giving the music a greater sense of depth and three-dimensionality.</p>\r\n<p>Voice Mode: Makes voices clearer and increases the volume level. Designed for enjoying TV shows, news, and more.</p>\r\n<p>4K Pass-Through</p>\r\n<p>Compatible with 4K HDR and Dolby Vision to allow you to enjoy the latest movie formats in stunning quality.</p>\r\n<p>HDMI ARC</p>\r\n<p><span data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i6.1b8b49b9knyKJo@>Simplify your setup by using a single HDMI cable to connect Infini Pro to your TV&rsquo;s ARC port and control volume using your TV&rsquo;s remote.</span></p>\r\n<p>Dolby Atmos requires HDMI passthrough from a Dolby Atmos-Compatible source device.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 07:55:36', '2021-09-18 08:43:38', NULL, NULL),
(259, 'Anker SoundCore Life P2', 'A3919011', 'anker-soundcore-life-p2', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 26, 1, 1, 1, '5350', '5800', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1629869977121022772.jpg,1630220153553664952.jpg,1630220153933372680.jpg,1630220153224617396.jpg,1630220153828026848.jpg,1630220153519407555.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Perfect for Home Offices</strong>: Each earbud has two microphones with beamforming noise reduction and cVc 8.0 technology for superior vocal enhancement and background-noise suppression.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Incredible Sound Powered By Graphene Drivers</strong>: Delivers music with a wider soundstage and exceptional accuracy and clarity. BassUp technology enhances bass by up to 43% and aptX audio offers lossless transmission between your device and the wireless earbuds.</p>\r\n<p><span class=@a-text-bold@><strong>aptX Technology:</strong>&nbsp;</span>Your music is transferred at the highest possible quality to preserve the sound and give you an exceptional listening experience with CD-like audio quality.</p>\r\n<p><strong>40-Hour Playtime with Fast Charge</strong>: A single charge gives you a full 7 hours of listening, while the charging case extends that to 40 hours. When you&rsquo;re in a rush and need power fast, simply charge for 10 minutes and get up to 1 hour of playtime.</p>\r\n<p><strong>IPX7 waterproof</strong>: life P2 wireless earbuds boast ipx7-rated protection that defends against liquids in any weather conditions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>One-Step Pairing</strong>: Our proprietary PUSH AND GO technology streamlines the setup process so when you remove the wireless earbuds from the charging case, they&rsquo;ll automatically connect to the last paired device.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Brand Name: <strong>ANKER</strong></p>\r\n<p>Style: <strong>In-Ear</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vocalism Principle: <strong>Dynamic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Origin: <strong>CN(Origin)</strong></p>\r\n<p>Control Button: <strong>Yes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Active Noise-Cancellation: <strong>No</strong></p>\r\n<p>Communication: <strong>Wireless</strong></p>\r\n<p>Volume Control: <strong>No</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sensitivity: <strong>96dBdB</strong></p>\r\n<p>Wireless Type: <strong>Bluetooth</strong></p>\r\n<p>Is wireless: <strong>Yes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Support APP: <strong>No</strong></p>\r\n<p>Function: <strong>Common Headphone</strong></p>\r\n<p>Connectors: <strong>None</strong></p>\r\n<p>Model Number: <strong>A3919</strong></p>\r\n<p>Codecs: <strong>Apt-X</strong></p>\r\n<p>Support Memory Card: <strong>No</strong></p>\r\n<p>Resistance: <strong>16&Omega;&Omega;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Waterproof: <strong>Yes</strong></p>\r\n<p>With Microphone: <strong>Yes</strong></p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 08:18:52', '2021-09-18 08:44:12', NULL, NULL),
(260, 'Anker SoundCore Spirit X (Black)', 'A3451012', 'anker-soundcore-spirit-x-black', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 26, 1, 1, 1, '2850', '3100', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1629870773632075736.jpg,1630220339899810983.jpg,1630220339247640999.jpg,1630220340344883374.jpg,1630220340259259660.jpg,1630220340907288750.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Better than IPX</strong><br />Even the highest IPX-ratings are simply not enough to defend against the corrosive power of sweat. Spirit X implements a submarine-inspired structure and impermeable hydro-seal to create an impervious barrier around the sensitive internal components.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Effortless Comfort</strong><br />When you are laser focused on grinding out the final rep or sprinting the last stretch, Spirit X sit almost unnoticed, fueling your effort with stunning sound.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hold Fast, Go Fast</strong><br />Ensure your tunes hold firm as you sprint, jump, and flip through your workout. No matter how close you go to your limit, Spirit X are to stay in place.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Powerful Audio Fuel</strong><br />Expanded 10 mm dynamic drivers work like a piston to force hard-hitting bass that leaves you with no choice but to maintain relentless workout intensity. Precision in-house tuning ensures Spirit X&rsquo;s deep low-end is balanced by lush midst and crystal-clear treble.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Get Unrivaled Stamina</strong><br />Using exclusive Anker charging technology, Spirit X will play for over up to 12 hours from a single charge. That&rsquo;s almost 250 songs or over a week of workouts from a 1.5 hour charge.&nbsp;</p>', '<table class=@apm-tablemodule-table@ cellspacing=@0@ cellpadding=@0@>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-imagerows@>\r\n<th><a href=@https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07BMV5T2N/ref=emc_b_5_t@>Soundcore Spirit Pro</a></th>\r\n<th><a href=@https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07BHHB5RH/ref=emc_b_5_t@>Soundcore Spirit</a></th>\r\n<th><a href=@https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07B9R67WR/ref=emc_b_5_t@>Soundcore Spirit X</a></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@>&nbsp;</th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>A3402</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>A3403</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>A3451</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Design</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>Ergonomic In-Ear</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>Ergonomic In-Ear</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>In-Ear Earhook</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Sound</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>6 mm Drivers + Dual EQ Modes (Crystal-Clear Sound with Deeper Bass)</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>6.1 mm Drivers (Crystal-Clear Sound)</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>10 mm Drivers (Well-Balanced Sound)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Playtime (Varies according to volume level &amp; audio content)@</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>Up to 10 Hours (at 60% Volume)</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>Up to 8 Hours (at 60% Volume)</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>Up to 12 Hours (at 60% Volume)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Bluetooth</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>V 4.2</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>V 5.0</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>V 5.0</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Supported Bluetooth Codec</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>aptX, AAC, SBC</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>AAC, SBC</span></td>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell selected@><span class=@a-size-base@>AAC, SBC</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=@apm-tablemodule-keyvalue@>\r\n<th class=@apm-tablemodule-keyhead@><span class=@a-size-base a-text-normal a-color-secondary@>Features</span></th>\r\n<td class=@apm-tablemodule-valuecell@><span class=@a-size-base@>SweatGuard / aptX Hi-Res HD Sound / Dual EQ Mode</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-08-24 08:39:14', '2021-09-18 08:44:43', NULL, NULL),
(261, 'Anker SoundCore Liberty Air 2 Pro', 'A3951011', 'anker-soundcore-liberty-air-2-pro', 'standard', 'C128', 197, 26, 1, 1, 1, '11600', '12490', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1629869666641886693.jpg,1630220030603855203.jpg,1630220031892087343.jpg,1630220031511517802.jpg,1630220031122741336.jpg,1630220031453911580.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@><span data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i3.a277741e38iPmV@>Targeted Active Noise Cancelling: Designed to eliminate the most disruptive and intrusive noise in everyday situations; choose from Transport, Outdoor, and Indoor modes.</span></p>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@>HearID Customized Sound: Hearing and ear analysis that intelligently creates your ideal listening profile for sublime sound. Also includes complete EQ control and 22 preset EQs.</p>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@>Charging Freedom: Charge via USB-C or a Qi Certified wireless charger. Put the buds in the case for 15 minutes for 3 hours of listening.</p>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@>Bluetooth 5.0: Super-strong and straightforward connectivity that pairs fast and stays stable.</p>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i4.a277741e38iPmV@>All-Day Comfort: Comes with 9 pairs of EarTips designed with super-soft silicone.</p>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8.0px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i5.a277741e38iPmV@>Auto Pause/Play: Sensors stop the music when the earbuds are removed and start it again when they are put back.</p>', '<p>Liberty Air 2 Pro True Wireless Earbuds</p>\r\n<p>Wireless Charging Case</p>\r\n<p>6 Mics for Calls, 26H Playtime</p>\r\n<p>9 EarTips XXXS/XXS/XS/S/M/M+/L/L+/XL</p>\r\n<p>60cm USB-C Cable</p>\r\n<p>Quick Start Guide</p>\r\n<p>Bran