(269, 'Lenovo HE05 wireless in-ear neckband earphones - Black', '06033925', 'lenovo-he05-wireless-in-ear-neckband-earphones-black', 'standard', 'C128', 196, 26, 1, 1, 1, '445', '500', -2, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630397623567487896.jpg,1632294448486873341.jpg,1632294448296695634.jpg,1632294448711984658.jpg,1632294448550053264.jpg,1632294448985002245.jpg,1632294448792028345.jpg,1632294448354139593.jpg,1632294448902916105.jpg,1632294448975406744.jpg,1632294448889473521.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>It features BT 5.0 technology, convenient for you to connect it to your smartphone, with CVC noise-canceling mic, the earphones get rid of static and environmental noises during phone calls, so that you can have clearer and more stable calls. Top grade loudspeakers, giving you all-around stereo sound, perfect for playing games. Built-in 80mAh rechargeable battery, giving it a standby time of 120 hours and continuous working time for about 8 hours. When connected to your phone, the battery capacity of the earphones will be shown on your phone so that you can know when to charge your earphoneseasily. With buttons on earphones, you can play / pause music, adjust volume and answer / end calls with one simple operation on the eardphones. Made from qualified metal and silicone material, it\'s dust-proof, sweatproof and waterproof, great for your daily use.</p>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p><strong>Type:</strong> In-Ear</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong> Metal, Silicone, TPE</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong> Surround Sound</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wearing type:</strong> Neckband</p>\r\n<p><strong>Main Functions:</strong> Answering Phone, Bluetooth, Microphone, Noise Cancelling, Sweatproof, Voice Prompt, Volume Control, Waterproof</p>\r\n<p><strong>Application:</strong> Running, Sport</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cable Length (m):</strong> 0.6m</p>\r\n<p><strong>Compat