(299, 'Haylou TWS T15 Bluetooth Earphone - Black', '35908745', 'haylou-tws-t15-bluetooth-earphone-black', 'standard', 'C128', 194, 26, 1, 1, 1, '1550', '1750', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630761923975212643.jpg,1632727262540864874.jpg,1632727262250427307.jpg,1632727262140498068.jpg,1632727262605073826.jpg,1632727262398124962.jpg,1632727262945919307.jpg,1632727262445983677.jpg,1632727263231081317.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>Mini True Wireless Noise Cancelling Earphone, Enjoy Long-time HiFi Music Haylou T15 Mini Bluetooth Earphone is one of the top picks for wireless music experience. Featuring the latest Bluetooth 5.0 protocol, the two earbuds stream audio instantly from your devices, including Bluetooth-enabled smartphones, tablets, laptops, and more. They can be used individually or simultaneously, reproducing great HiFi sound with DSP tech, and you just can\'t stop anymore. Don\'t worry about the battery life, the mini portable power bank can charge your phones, providing up to 60 hours of wireless music. Fill your life with wonderful melodies as you go.</p>\r\n<p>Main Features:</p>\r\n<p>●Flying bird bionic design, intelligent touch control, convenient operation, 3.7g comfortable wearing</p>\r\n<p>●2200mAh large capacity battery, can charge mobile phones, provide 60 hours long battery life</p>\r\n<p>● Intelligent real-time power display, high-sensitivity Hall switch control, open the top of the charging dock, you can easily check the remaining power</p>\r\n<p>●Master-slave switch, solved the problem of tedious and disconnected switching of single and double ears of true wireless headphones</p>\r\n<p>● DSP intelligent noise reduction, filter noise, anti-interference, high-definition sound quality</p>\r\n<p>● Bluetooth 5.0 true wireless, 3 times faster response, faster and more stable, delay reduced by 60%</p>\r\n<p>● Support game mode, music mode, call mode, voice assistant</p>\r\n<p>●IPX5 all-round water-resistant and sweat-proof design, outstanding appearance, meanwhile have certain anti-drop performance</p>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@><span data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i2.7ae625bC25bCuG@>Brand: Haylou</span></div>\r\n<div class=@html-content detail-content@>\r\n<p>Model Number: T15</p>\r\n<p>Earphones type: Earphone</p>\r\n<p>Materials: ABS</p>\r\n<p>Mainly Compatible with: Blackberry,HTC,iPad,iPhone,iPod,LG,Motorola,Nokia,SAMSUNG,Sony Ericsson</p>\r\n<p>Functions: English voice prompt,Phone call answering,Song switch,Support music,Voice control</p>\r\n<p>Bluetooth Version: V5.0</p>\r\n<p>Bluetooth protocol: A2DP,AVRCP,HEP v1.6,HSP</p>\r\n<p>Transmission range: 10 meters</p>\r\n<p>Battery Capacity (mAh): 43mAh per earphone, 2200mAh charging dock</p>\r\n<p>Charging Time: 1.5 hours for earphone, 4 hours for charging dock</p>\r\n<p>Talking Time: 100 hours</p>\r\n<p>Audio: Stereo</p>\r\n<p>Color: Black</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-09-04 08:05:12', '2021-09-27 07:21:55', NULL, NULL),
