(308, 'Huawei HONOR Router 3 Dual-core WiFi6+ 4 Antenna Intelligent – White', '09586433', 'huawei-honor-router-3-dual-core-wifi6-4-antenna-intelligent-white-1', 'standard', 'C128', 208, 40, 1, 1, 1, '4390', '4750', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1630746495791199748.jpg,1631185525420457980.jpg,1631185525789792629.jpg,1631185525620921184.jpeg,1631185525227350106.jpg,1631185991206713609.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@pdp-product-desc @ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i1.51ddafSOafSObC@>\r\n<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>HONOOR Wi-Fi 6-enabled phones are able to send 5dBi stronger signals back to HONOR Router 3 in stable, 2 MHz narrow bandwidth using Dynamic Narrow Bandwidth technology, which is based on Chipset Synergy. The wireless signals can penetrate solid objects like walls and floors easily. This means that the phone will have good reception of the Wi-Fi signal, even when connecting from upstairs or somewhere far from the router. Larger Bandwidth with 160 MHz.</p>\r\n<p>As HONOR Router 3 supports 160 MHz, when connecting Router 3 to devices supporting 160 MHz, like top-of-the-line HUAWEI Wi-Fi 5-enabled smart phones, tablets and laptops, the internet speed would increase by 60% and more. This offers you an unprecedented, lag-free experience on mobile devices. HONOR Router 3 offers a secure area inside its main processor, where both software and hardware are used to protect the data , meaning it could operate safely in a commercial environment, offering great security assurance to your devices.</p>\r\n<p>When the Huawei Hilink device is connected to the Internet through the APP, password-free access is more convenient;When the router Wi-Fi name/password is modified, the router will automatically synchronize to the connected Huawei HiLink device.There is no need to reconnect to the network one by one.</p>\r\n<p>Its theoretical speed can reach up to 3000 Mbps (574 Mbps on a 2.4 GHz band and 2402 Mbps on a 5 GHz band).The Dual-core Gigahome CPU allows HONOR Router 3 to best unleash its speed. At such speed, what used to be taken for granted, like buffering and lagging, will be a thing of the past. Enjoy smooth streaming and gaming like never before.</p>\r\n<p>HONOR Router 3 and Wi-Fi 6-enabled HONOR 30 series phones are the perfect pair because both are equipped with HUAWEI\'s self-developed Wi-Fi chipset, which support 160 MHz frequency bandwidth,This lays the foundation for Chipset Synergy, bringing out optimal speed and efficiency.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>Brand: Huawei</p>\r\n<p>Model Name: HONOR WiFi Router 3,</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@html-content detail-content@>\r\n<p>Dimensions: 242mm x 151.9mm x 40.9 mm,</p>\r\n<p>Weight: About 379g,</p>\r\n<p>Processors: Gigahome Dual-core 1.2 GHz CPU,</p>\r\n<p>Power Supply: 12 V DC, 1 A; Consumption &lt; 12 W,</p>\r\n<p>RAM + ROM: 128MB+128MB,</p>\r\n<p>H button for one-key pairing and WPS compatible,</p>\r\n<p>Independent Reset,</p>\r\n<p>Interface: 802.11ax/ac/n/a 2 x 2 &amp; 802.11ax/n/b/g 2 x 2, MU-MIMO,</p>\r\n<p>Wireless speed is up to 2976 Mbps (2.4 GHz: 574 Mbps; 5 GHz: 2402 Mbps)</p>\r\n<p>Software: APP: HUAWEI AI Life App, Huawei Share (Tap to Connect), Huawei HiLink &amp; 802.11v protocol, IPv4 / IPv6, PPPoE / DHCP / static IP address / Bridge WAN connection methods, Wi-Fi timer, Guest Wi-Fi, Device speed limiting, MAC address filter, Parental control, VPN pass-through, DMZ / virtual server. Security TrustZone Security, Anti-brute force algorithms, Firewall, DMZ, DoS attack protection</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2021-09-04 09:04:33', '2021-09-18 09:03:38', NULL, NULL),
