(327, 'Mi Smart LED Bulb Essential (White and Color)', '24170936', 'mi-smart-led-bulb-essential-white-and-color', 'standard', 'C128', 192, 39, 1, 1, 1, '930', '1050', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631013911883784405.jpg,1632740215934115677.jpg,1632740215977360816.jpg,1632740215956756674.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p style=@font-style: normal; text-align: start;@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i4.7f22w8etw8etY6@>Why choose a Xiaomi smart bulb?</p>\r\n<div class=@pdp-product-detail@ data-spm=@product_detail@>\r\n<div class=@pdp-product-desc height-limit@>\r\n<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>Up to 16 million colors</p>\r\n<p>Easy to install Adjustable color temperature according to room or mood (1700 &ndash; 6500K)</p>\r\n<p>Easy to use through the app, no control unit is required</p>\r\n<p>Control via Google Assistant, Amazon Alexa</p>\r\n<h2 style=@font-style: normal; text-align: start;@>Really handy bulb</h2>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i1.7f22w8etw8etY6@>With the Xiaomi Home App / Mi Home App intelligent control, you can control and adjust bulb functions such as timing, multi-light control, or sunrise mode. If you&rsquo;re one of those forgetful ones, that&rsquo;s not a problem either. When you leave the house, you can easily see if you have forgotten to turn off the lights. If so, there will be nothing easier than turning them off comfortably, for example, from work. You can also adjust the brightness and color temperature, allowing you to change them according to your mood or situation.</p>\r\n<div style=@box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; margin: 0; padding: 8px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=@font-style: normal; text-align: start;@>Morning or evening?</h2>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@ data-spm-anchor-id=@a2a0e.pdp.product_detail.i2.7f22w8etw8etY6@>You can pre-set four lights and dimmer for the switch that comes with the bulb, making it even easier to use. In a second, you can adjust light when laughing or bad weather. The color range has up to 16 million colors, so creativity is not limited and at home you can create a truly professional lighting for watching a movie or celebrating a birthday.</p>\r\n<h2 style=@font-style: normal; text-align: start;@>Voice control</h2>\r\n<p style=@margin: 0; padding: 8px 0; white-space: pre-wrap;@>Light bulb easily work with Google Assistant or Amazon Alexa. Use your voice to turn light on or off, change color, color temperature and brightness.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<p><strong>Model:</strong>MJDPL01YL</p>\r\n<p><strong>Luminous Flux:</strong>950 lumens</p>\r\n<p><strong>Color Temperature Range:</strong>1700&ndash;6500 K</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lamp Fitting:</strong>E27</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rated Input:</strong>220-240 V ~ 50/60 Hz 0.07 A</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rated Power:</strong>9 W</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions:</strong>&phi;55 &times; 120 mm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Service Life:</strong>Approx.25,000 h</p>\r\n<p><strong>On/off：</strong>125000 Cycles</p>\r\n<p><strong>Operating Temperature:</strong>-10&deg;C to 40&deg;C</p>\r\n<p><strong>Operating Humidity:</strong>0&ndash;85% RH</p>\r\n<p><strong>Operating Frequency:</strong>2412&ndash;2472 MHz</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Output Power:</strong>17.41 dBm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wireless Connectivity:</strong> Wi-Fi IEEE 802.11 b/g/n 2.4 GHz</p>\r\n<p><strong>Compatible with:</strong> Android 4.4, iOS 9.0 or above</p>\r\n<p><strong>Package Contents:</strong> Mi LED Smart Bulb Essential (White and Color), user manual,</p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-09-05 07:19:36', '2021-09-27 10:57:09', NULL, NULL),
