(375, 'Mi Dual Mode Wireless Mouse (Silent Edition) - Black', '35976120', 'mi-dual-mode-wireless-mouse-silent-edition-black', 'standard', 'C128', 192, 29, 1, 1, 1, '1150', '1300', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631171135337742157.jpg,1632736632584505364.jpg,1632736632142695876.jpg,1632736632780885721.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@pdp-product-detail@ data-spm=@product_detail@>\r\n<div class=@pdp-product-desc height-limit@>\r\n<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>Bluetooth + 2.4GHz dual-mode connection, wireless office freer. Dual-mode wireless mouse, get rid of the shackles of cables, make your desktop clean and efficient, and double the daily office efficiency. Support 2.4GHz wireless receiver and Bluetooth dual-mode can be connected to two computers, just press the mode switch button on the front of the mouse to switch freely between the two computers. The practical mute button design will no longer let the disturbing @click@ sound make you the focus of everyone, allowing you to remain calm and polite whether you are in the office, conference room, or library, and other quiet places. Even if you work from home until late at night, it will not disturb your family&rsquo;s rest. More intimate side button design, convenient and practical forward and backward.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<p>The practical shortcut keys on the left support the easy realization of one-key forward and one-key backward functions on the Windows system, making it easier and more efficient for office work or web browsing. The ergonomic&nbsp;design makes operation more comfortable .</p>\r\n<p>UV skin-friendly coating top cover, plastic etched body, with fading dot texture, stable operation and not easy to slip, even sweat will not affect the grip. Just the right size, customized for Asian hands.</p>\r\n<p>Design is not only about aesthetic expression, but also the precise accumulation of data. We have conducted repeated studies on the structure and size of Asian hands, and only then have we got the fit curve and feel that makes you feel just right. There is no heavy burden even after long-term use, it is so considerate.</p>\r\n<p>More intimate shape design, to ensure the grip and also beautiful. The symmetrical shape and the slightly waisted mid-section design not only meet the visual needs, but also provide the right grip.</p>\r\n<p>Power supply: 2 x AAA batteries (not included).</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2021-09-05 12:08:20', '2021-09-27 09:57:50', NULL, NULL),
(377, 'MI TV Indian 4A 40 inch FHD (L40M5-5AIN) - Global Version', '49269609', 'mi-tv-indian-4a-40-inch-fhd-l40m5-5ain-global-version', 'standard', 'C128', 192, 39, 1, 1, 1, '33000', '34990', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631171377745765383.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@pdp-product-detail@ data-spm=@product_detail@>\r\n<div class=@pdp-product-desc height-limit@>\r\n<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>40-inch FHD Display, IPS Display Panel, Running On Android OS With PatchWall UI, Amlogic Quad-core Processor, Mali-450 MP3 GPU, 1 GB RAM &amp; 8 GB Internal Storage.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<p>Built-in Wifi &amp; Ethernet Port. 10W Dual Speakers, DTH-HD,Dolby Digital Surround Sound, Google Smart Assistant, Data Saving Technology.</p>', 1, 0, 1, 0, '2021-09-05 12:15:32', '2021-09-18 09:21:27', NULL, NULL),
(379, 'Mi Curved Gaming Monitor 34 inch Black', '22024476', 'mi-curved-gaming-monitor-34-inch-black', 'standard', 'C128', 192, 31, 1, 1, 1, '41000', '45000', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631170841887801386.jpg,1631170841887801386.jpg,1631170841887801386.jpg,1631170841887801386.jpg,1631170841887801386.jpg,1631170841887801386.jpg,1632735142180295656.jpg,1632735143535732652.jpg,1632735143467750358.jpg,1632735143736914304.jpg,1632735143789267390.jpg,1632735143632158741.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=@pdp-product-desc height-limit@>\r\n<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>21:9 wide panoramic view. The 21:9 format of the game interface is 30% wider than the average 16:9 screen player\'s field of view, especially in RTS and FPS games, the field of vision is extremely wide. Ultra clear image with clear details. 3440&times;1440 ultra-clear resolution, every corner of the scene can be realistic and delicate, and the game world is spectacular and exquisite. High brightness, high contrast, and vivid picture quality. The display brightness is up to 300 nits, with a high contrast ratio of 3000:1, the game screen is from bright white to deep black, clear and beautiful, vivid and vivid.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=@html-content pdp-product-highlights@>\r\n<p>1500R large curvature surrounded the visual field, gives you an immersive experience.</p>\r\n<p>The 1500R\'s extremely large curvature design, the line of sight is surrounded by the screen, showing a panoramic view of the overall immersion;</p>\r\n<p>the curved screen has a smaller visual tilt angle, and the eyes are almost equidistant, reducing visual distortion, fully restore the true Horizons of each corner. 144Hz high refresh rate, fast responses, every action is faster.</p>\r\n<p>144Hz high refresh rate, 4ms response time, effectively reduce game picture stagnation and smear.</p>\r\n<p>Shooting games that require a quick response are more likely to lock the target and hit the enemy with precisions.</p>\r\n<p>AMD Free-Sync, the picture is smooth, not stuck, not tearing. AMD Free-Sync technology can consistently match the screen display at high frame rate input, reducing problems such as stucking or tearing during gameplay, improving visual fluency, and greatly enhancing player competitiveness.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=@html-content detail-content@>&nbsp;</div>', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2021-09-05 12:18:39', '2021-09-27 09:32:23', NULL, NULL),
(381, 'Amazfit power buds Heart Rate Monitoring Sports Earbuds -Black', '52749258', 'amazfit-power-buds-heart-rate-monitoring-sports-earbuds-black', 'standard', 'C128', 210, 26, 1, 1, 1, '5650', '6700', 1, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631613096660548067.jpeg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Heart Rate Monitoring During Exercise<sup>. </sup>Workout Safer and More Effectively, Magnetic Sport Ear Hooks, Firm &amp; Comfortable, Tailored to Exercise. Professional Sports Sound System, Immersive and Dynamic Sound to Accompany Your Movement. Abundant Power to Boost Energy, 24 Hours of Music On-the-go. IP55 Water- and Dust-resistance. No Fear of Dust, Rain or Sweat. Quick Auto-pairing &amp; In-ear Detection. All You Have to Do Is Put Them In.ENC Dual-microphone Noise-reduction. Filter Ambient Noise for HD Calls. Intuitive Touch Controls. Operate with A Gentle Tap. The battery life is about 8 hours on a single charge. The charging box can provide about 16 hours of battery life, and the total battery life is about 24 hours. And in the heart rate monitoring off mode, 15 minutes of charging can have 3 hours of battery life.</p>', '<div class=@woocommerce-product-details__short-description@>\r\n<p>Brand: Amazfit</p>\r\n<p>Model : Earbuds A1965; Charging case A1967</p>\r\n<p>Battery Capacity : Earbuds 55mAh;</p>\r\n<p>Charging case : 450mAh</p>\r\n<p>Input : Earbuds 5V 0.12A;</p>\r\n<p>Charging case : 5V 0.5A</p>\r\n<p>System requirements : Android 5.0 or iOS 10.0 and above</p>\r\n<p>Wireless connection : Dual-core Bluetooth chips, BT5.0 BLE</p>\r\n<p>Weight : Earbuds 6g x 2, total (box + earbuds + hooks) 69g</p>\r\n<p>Water &amp; dust resistance : IP55 (Earbuds)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-09-14 07:58:27', '2022-01-29 10:06:54', NULL, NULL),
(382, 'Mi WiFi Router 4A AC1200 Dual Band-1167 Mbps Gigabit Version - Global Edition', '26341450', 'mi-wifi-router-4a-ac1200-dual-band-1167-mbps-gigabit-version-global-edition', 'standard', 'C128', 192, 40, 1, 1, 1, '2480', '2750', 0, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1631695570779354921.jpg,1633159299617228492.jpg,1633159299975306499.jpg,1633159299843012953.jpg,1633159299289350718.jpg,1633159299545217329.jpg,1633159299714590986.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>1 x Gigabit WAN port + 2 x Gigabit LAN ports, easily meet the fiber broadband of 100M and above access requirements, 2-core 4-thread CPU, 880MHz main frequency, fast internet access and fluent internet surfing, 1167MHz dual-band concurrent rate, no-interface, Supported5 GHz WiFi Channels :36, 40, 44, 48, Same name for dual frequency, automatic access the optimal frequency</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Model: Xiaomi</p>\r\n<p>Integrated signal amplifier, wider coverage and faster transmission distance</p>\r\n<p>128MB large memory, support 128 terminal devices connection</p>\r\n<p>Intelligent error correction algorithm to improve weak signal</p>\r\n<p>manage your child\'s online time and content, protect your child\'s Internet security</p>\r\n<p>Set the device\'s networkable time and the range of URLs allowed to access</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-09-15 08:46:10', '2021-10-02 07:22:08', NULL, NULL),
(383, 'Baseus 65W Power Bank 30000mAh PowerBank PPLG-A01 Fast Charging PD', '41128578', 'baseus-65w-power-bank-30000mah-powerbank-pplg-a01-fast-charging-pd', 'standard', 'C128', 193, 27, 1, 1, 1, '3700', '3999', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '1632395759593545250.jpg,1632395810192279952.jpg,1632395810730750456.jpg,1632395810751869170.jpg,1632395810884612056.jpg,1632395810512920275.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>BASEUS 30000mAh Power Bank Fast Charging Charger Digital Display Screen Portable Charger &ndash; Black, With large capacity of 30000mAh, enough for charging the device many times to eliminate the anxiety of battery exhaustion, 65W Larger output, fast charging time, save much of your time, Digital display screen for showing remaining capacity power, With 5 outputs, easy to charge 5 devices at the same time, it can be also used to charge your laptop computer (MAC and Others) , Mini and compact, convenient to carry, ideal for traveling usage.</p>', '<p>Battery Capacity:&nbsp;About 30000mAh/3.8V</p>\r\n<p>Rated Capacity:&nbsp;About 18000mAh</p>\r\n<p data-spm-anchor-id=@a2g0o.detail.1000023.i0.24c9582e2zXova@>Energy Conversion:&nbsp;About &ge;78%</p>\r\n<p>Input:<br />Micro: 5V/2A&nbsp; 9V/2A&nbsp; 12V/1.5A&nbsp; 18W Max.<br />Type-C: 5V/3A&nbsp; 9V/3A&nbsp; 12V/3A&nbsp; 15V/3A&nbsp; 20V/3A&nbsp; 60W Max.<br />For iP : 5V/2.1A</p>\r\n<p><br />Output:<br />USB4: 5V/4.5A&nbsp; 4.5V/5A&nbsp; 5V/3A&nbsp; 9V/3A&nbsp; 12V/2.5A&nbsp; 20V/1.5A 30W Max.<br />USB1/USB2/USB3: 5V/3A&nbsp; 15W Max.<br />USB1/USB2/USB3+USB4: 5V/3A&nbsp; 15W Max.<br />Type-C: 5V/3A&nbsp; 9V/3A&nbsp; 12V/3A&nbsp; 15V/3A&nbsp; 20V/3.25A&nbsp; 65W Max.<br />USB1/USB2/USB3+Type-C:5V/3A+45W<br />USB4+Type-C:18W+45W<br />USB1-USB4+Type-C:15W+45W<br />Total output: 5V/6A<br />Size: 145*65*38mm</p>\r\n<p>Weight: 550g</p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2021-09-23 10:58:51', '2021-10-26 06:44:31', NULL, NULL),
